{"tid":2311305,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"給肥佬黎的信  #社評","createTime":"2020-12-04T03:15:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T14:54:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d93df75ae8fe80bdcce2cb0c711ba25f67b2fec1","tid":2311305,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T03:15:09.000Z","msg":"給肥佬黎的信 <br />\n#社評<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DHYzuyo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDHYzuyo.jpg&h=12d16d5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9fa105d7f3fb9bfc8acdead3d1725107bd3a8fdd","tid":2311305,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d93df75ae8fe80bdcce2cb0c711ba25f67b2fec1","tid":2311305,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T03:15:09.000Z","msg":"給肥佬黎的信 <br />\n#社評<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DHYzuyo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDHYzuyo.jpg&h=12d16d5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T04:11:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201204/5QR3VVWPRFH2HBVZFIJVLHZBNA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201204%2F5QR3VVWPRFH2HBVZFIJVLHZBNA%2F&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGG1VrQWH3Jev0gRtxLi1IiE%3D&h=bc7cf0de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201204%2F5QR3VVWPRFH2HBVZFIJVLHZBNA%2F&h=cdb26487\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201204/5QR3VVWPRFH2HBVZFIJVLHZBNA/</a><br />\n<br />\n給肥佬黎的信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/F1FJX6PxlrWe5CYaXBRhIroRtxo=/5862x3918/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JFUZ64P7L5F6HKUHRCXNKFGKPI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FF1FJX6PxlrWe5CYaXBRhIroRtxo%3D%2F5862x3918%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJFUZ64P7L5F6HKUHRCXNKFGKPI.jpg&h=dd38f6bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎智英<br />\n<br />\n黎智英還柙期間，除了跟律師會面商討案件，每天只獲安排一名親友探望。他最喜愛的手機已被沒收，失去跟世界的大部份聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：大狀：保釋是人權 還柙須理由充份  未審先囚 多案違法律原則<br />\n<br />\n然而，收押所內肥佬黎每天仍可閱報，包括《蘋果日報》。若讀者們想為他加油打氣，不妨給他寫信，我們收到來信後，會把你們的心意刊登在《蘋果日報》，讓失去自由的黎智英能感受外界對他的支持。<br />\n<br />\n謝謝各位！<br />\n<br />\n（來信可寄將軍澳工業邨駿盈街八號一樓《蘋果日報》，或email至adnews@appledaily.com）"},{"pid":"87809a5598e510ea69b13e0c26b8f62262e681ce","tid":2311305,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T04:15:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26f2b4e2e3353c22ede805b131dc2f3e5f655346","tid":2311305,"uid":1989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T04:51:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d281fbc82d882e36011f62b13cfcad017f5a52df","tid":2311305,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T05:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c56eee43f3225fd9453d5589b4dbdae376a8fbf1","tid":2311305,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T07:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6abfcb83e4e8cd7687d440060c2e3b9f6c5e7ca","tid":2311305,"uid":262557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T07:17:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49dba7b9ac0510bb08f0955b1ea588d6da6d4634","tid":2311305,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T09:30:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8589c086da2c7ea0c301bbb4cbf55