5,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T02:29:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ndfR3xg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FndfR3xg.jpg&h=299e82e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6b1353534c0a5a2995b05bcdb8b11e9fe786fe7","tid":2311305,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T02:28:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kw7EAYH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKw7EAYH.jpg&h=0ee72ad5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8dca0fc0a6c45c8df6d3a6b99986cf37c816491b","tid":2311305,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T09:24:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201209/V6GY7MF655HR7DDWBWG6YT76AE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201209%2FV6GY7MF655HR7DDWBWG6YT76AE%2F&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGG1VrQWH3Jev0gRtxLi1IiE%3D&h=b8272aa3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201209%2FV6GY7MF655HR7DDWBWG6YT76AE%2F&h=fa7b1bc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201209/V6GY7MF655HR7DDWBWG6YT76AE/</a><br />\n<br />\n你的堅持 我畢生受用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_lqC29hwT1Mv_hv3e57Phw0sqFY=/1772x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FJDRLFE5SZFS3M7KBZONVGMXHQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_lqC29hwT1Mv_hv3e57Phw0sqFY%3D%2F1772x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFJDRLFE5SZFS3M7KBZONVGMXHQ.jpg&h=14a205de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有《蘋果日報》員工依創刊電視廣告繪圖，盼黎智英仍像25年前般，&ldquo;No fear we have to fight on.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n黎智英昨天在收押所度過73歲生日，也是他被關押的第六天。連日來香港人送上的祝福從無間斷，有掛念他的手足、有嚮往公平公義的年輕人，也有同業的共勉。有讀者更打趣叫「肥佬黎」在收押所化身「記者」發掘「猛料」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：「佢唔諗自己，只睇點樣幫大家」<br />\n<br />\n祝福以外，更多人感謝黎智英以生命影響生命。有讀者從《蘋果日報》、《壹週刊》中學懂反思，分辨是非；有年輕人牢記黎智英說過不移民、不離開，也決心留在香港。有海外留學生從沒忘記黎智英在香港最艱難時刻的堅持，「對我來說是畢生受用」。<br />\n<br />\n每一封寄給黎智英的信，都在訴說一個故事。有大學生說，小時候父親每天都買《蘋果日報》，一買就多年，去年更與父親一起訂閱蘋果，「自由有價，自然新聞也應有價」。他說一直都希望為香港做些事，但在今日香港，會思考自己的付出是否值得，「在極度壓迫的環境下為求生存而放棄的是否值得」。<br />\n<br />\n當眼見很多同學朋友都移民外地，他卻記得黎智英在訪問中說過不移民、不離開，不久前他便決心留在香港，「黎先生，蘋果在香港人爭取民主、自由與真相的道路上從沒缺席。而你本人也對香港不離不棄。自然，當您身受牢獄之災時，港人也必定不會放棄您、放棄自己、放棄香港，如此黎先生也可放心。希望上主憐恤眾人，保守您和其他入獄手足的身體健康。願能早日相見」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QgSSzX3NaPKBpQ4732h8JG_UmVw=/777x904/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CLM5UL6UWBCCNOSVC2AJGTXCPE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQgSSzX3NaPKBpQ4732h8JG_UmVw%3D%2F777x904%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCLM5UL6UWBCCNOSVC2AJGTXCPE.gif&h=36ccb19f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一如既往 不會屈服<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WzongeTlyxjRtHmGJpYvLnr_bws=/606x507/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SJNTHI5Q2BBDFGBMNB4FIBPLIM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWzongeTlyxjRtHmGJpYvLnr_bws%3D%2F606x507%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSJNTHI5Q2BBDFGBMNB4FIBPLIM.gif&h=e197a0a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nProud of you, as always<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2sBsHtiJ2LSLt1V0WCV4ILwOmi0=/674x826/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KARNIRXOS5GNDGE2VMNVRMATF4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2sBsHtiJ2LSLt1V0WCV4ILwOmi0%3D%2F674x826%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKARNIRXOS5GNDGE2VMNVRMATF4.gif&h=ce3f7a8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n祝安寧度過黑暗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fvqPzaUMs_xOKlVd6k-3FNTW9mE=/590x755/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O4PUFL3D7RDMPAPTOAFSIBAMGY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfvqPzaUMs_xOKlVd6k-3FNTW9mE%3D%2F590x755%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO4PUFL3D7RDMPAPTOAFSIBAMGY.gif&h=0c152137&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上帝與你同在<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Te9W7BEa3NGdVyzUlQfMlXgrFLA=/706x382/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YPL4PJ2UFRDSHMXQBQ6ZCIHEQY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTe9W7BEa3NGdVyzUlQfMlXgrFLA%3D%2F706x382%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYPL4PJ2UFRDSHMXQBQ6ZCIHEQY.gif&h=7a91269e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當權者良心泯滅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eTCStllZEE44IbV3kTasteN34Ig=/701x478/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/L5ZJK3YSLZGVRA3PTJF6HCMI5U.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeTCStllZEE44IbV3kTasteN34Ig%3D%2F701x478%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FL5ZJK3YSLZGVRA3PTJF6HCMI5U.gif&h=820f9249&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港人永遠在你身邊"},{"pid":"a92187b90972b7d61e621de59375dcc4e1ffc986","tid":2311305,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T12:41:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201210/JCGDJBOGKNAK7J6S4HBTYLJAXI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201210%2FJCGDJBOGKNAK7J6S4HBTYLJAXI%2F&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGG1VrQWH3Jev0gRtxLi1IiE%3D&h=2c456158\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201210%2FJCGDJBOGKNAK7J6S4HBTYLJAXI%2F&h=bac902e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201210/JCGDJBOGKNAK7J6S4HBTYLJAXI/</a><br />\n<br />\n你唔放棄HK人 我哋唔會放棄你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/u-ZpWehYWNspftMw-zSCQ-Soc08=/1767x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AD4MS3QEXFBBDO3T7QRFT7R3TI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fu-ZpWehYWNspftMw-zSCQ-Soc08%3D%2F1767x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAD4MS3QEXFBBDO3T7QRFT7R3TI.jpg&h=5b3a0ce2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黎智英對讀者連日親筆來信表示感激。<br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒集團創辦人黎智英被控欺詐罪，遭關押荔枝角收押所至今一周，一眾老讀者、舊戰友，還有新相識的年輕人都堅持親筆來信，為他打氣加油。有教師洋洋六頁紙訴說百般滋味在心頭，並引聖經經文與黎智英共勉；有從前不理政治的新移民來信叫「肥佬」加油，一字一句都是繁體字，「就算沒有錢食飯，都要買蘋果日報」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：黎智英本周復看《蘋果》：謝讀者祝福<br />\n今時今日，執筆提字的人很少，寫給「肥佬黎」的信卻很多。其中讀者C小姐親筆的一封信長達六頁紙，跟「肥佬」訴說感受。她說除了訂閱蘋果動新聞外，每天都會買一份《蘋果日報》，也看見有些黃店放滿了《蘋果日報》以示支持，「您的堅持實在令不少香港人動容，亦鼓勵我學習您的堅持」。<br />\n<br />\n除了C小姐，開宗明義「N年無拎筆之人」則寫了一封英文信給「肥佬黎」，老實不客氣指他在部份人眼中或許不是好人，但對所有真香港人而言，絕對是好人一個。她說，過去兩年生活過得不順，但對比起香港這個家所經歷的事，只是小事一樁，她會努力克服困難，所以「肥佬」都要好好保重。<br />\n<br />\n「200+1香港人」也說，良久沒提筆寫信予親人，感覺有點陌生，「相信夢中驚醒的，徹夜難眠的，寒夜醒來的非只有這一撮人」。他說三人行必有黃絲，寄語被扣押的「親人」，「只要內心無懼，自然強，腰板挺直，風骨正」，大事大非更要心境明淨。有讀者自言不懂大道理，「但我知乜嘢係良心、公義」，來信快人快語，「你唔放棄HK人，我哋都唔會放棄你，支持你，加油！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cATIJlfAnR8WVAa28jxReZvYPAQ=/1759x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7M4GYUBWGZD2VEOLQJQA7VTCQY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcATIJlfAnR8WVAa28jxReZvYPAQ%3D%2F1759x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7M4GYUBWGZD2VEOLQJQA7VTCQY.jpg&h=283e77fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■除親筆信外，有讀者更獻上畫作，着黎智英如壁虎般「撐實」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/CQmX8exShW4N1HRZxa97DFCz0Fk=/1174x1299/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FOWDDTKX2JDFXLQSYEA5VC5PHI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCQmX8exShW4N1HRZxa97DFCz0Fk%3D%2F1174x1299%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFOWDDTKX2JDFXLQSYEA5VC5PHI.gif&h=bd9612d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n腰板挺直風骨正<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WpxTBYUkuUY_-q-A0i578GJhlrs=/1435x1024/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KVMC36NXAJEEVHH3XXVFLH5DQE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWpxTBYUkuUY_-q-A0i578GJhlrs%3D%2F1435x1024%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKVMC36NXAJEEVHH3XXVFLH5DQE.gif&h=852b18dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎明總有天會來<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mfBUi2aqbRGRG8Up6KppyAjLG20=/1297x2034/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/325IFBMICZEH3IPQGA3TITVHO4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmfBUi2aqbRGRG8Up6KppyAjLG20%3D%2F1297x2034%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F325IFBMICZEH3IPQGA3TITVHO4.gif&h=aac70acc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港人以你為榮 盼有天與你相擁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XSSgnN0n78yn_c6-3COZ8y79igw=/944x1218/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EH3FLR6QTZGCHCGBSHLDSNHIZQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXSSgnN0n78yn_c6-3COZ8y79igw%3D%2F944x1218%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEH3FLR6QTZGCHCGBSHLDSNHIZQ.gif&h=7db50a59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不畏強權 報道真相<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MG4u5nYceHo64ADOpfl_6fhDka0=/1145x663/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7CUJGIKYIVGNZD2O7YCZMXN72E.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMG4u5nYceHo64ADOpfl_6fhDka0%3D%2F1145x663%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7CUJGIKYIVGNZD2O7YCZMXN72E.gif&h=b8c4cfc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每日買實體報支持"},{"pid":"cf2c718a86a709ee78d407cb5428485ae66a5b04","tid":2311305,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T09:06:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201211/7X4PWV6IWFECBJ5NNRHNYRCMTY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201211%2F7X4PWV6IWFECBJ5NNRHNYRCMTY%2F&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGG1VrQWH3Jev0gRtxLi1IiE%3D&h=f0a3c8af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201211%2F7X4PWV6IWFECBJ5NNRHNYRCMTY%2F&h=6645e370\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201211/7X4PWV6IWFECBJ5NNRHNYRCMTY/</a><br />\n<br />\n堅哥：我哋唔做契弟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Ma2sRTvN-_-tnpsdFo154231Coc=/1536x1024/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/55AWR4WAENBLTMYCHEKLAD6UWA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMa2sRTvN-_-tnpsdFo154231Coc%3D%2F1536x1024%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F55AWR4WAENBLTMYCHEKLAD6UWA.jpg&h=9d8ea590&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n葉一堅<br />\n<br />\n上周被落案控以欺詐罪的壹傳媒創辦人黎智英，關押荔枝角收押所至今逾一周。有老臣子及市民堅持寫上一封封「給肥佬黎的信」，為鐵窗內的黎智英送暖。與黎智英並肩作戰20年的壹傳媒非執行董事葉一堅，以「阿Dee」為下款談起昔日點滴，說黎智英過去多年說了很多次，「挑，賣《蘋果》？移民？我唔X想做契弟喎！」有讀者形容黎為小飛俠（Peter Pan），「永遠都有個小孩住進了心裏。亦常常追隨你的信念和熱情，面對逆境」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：黎智英：神畀嘅十字架欣然接受<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Sw-w19BUMayYuYQwHjTaH_Ki1T4=/5041x2377/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LKR7KB3NCZE6JBPNJ5ZEITZT5Y.GIF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSw-w19BUMayYuYQwHjTaH_Ki1T4%3D%2F5041x2377%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLKR7KB3NCZE6JBPNJ5ZEITZT5Y.GIF&h=c34d6a54&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e9419fc9c647c26859eff7310b7530b149dc995","tid":2311305,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T13:04:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原來！"},{"pid":"e42ca92a7c3af4d6b71cef9b91bd18d7976aeed8","tid":2311305,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T02:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nU3AGod.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnU3AGod.jpg&h=d9313425&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b285b38db239c1c7c0c06d0fcc1d3146df742a8a","tid":2311305,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T10:44:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201213/IBS6NSJXV5CLFG7R5S77ONQ72Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201213%2FIBS6NSJXV5CLFG7R5S77ONQ72Y%2F&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGG1VrQWH3Jev0gRtxLi1IiE%3D&h=6a3fe7de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201213%2FIBS6NSJXV5CLFG7R5S77ONQ72Y%2F&h=cac23c53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201213/IBS6NSJXV5CLFG7R5S77ONQ72Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n「感謝您為下一代，留下承受一切」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wdfjd2Y2K9Uxod_Io_8OilBEb6Y=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OV7B3C23RJEBNOENSCQ65VN7D4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fwdfjd2Y2K9Uxod_Io_8OilBEb6Y%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOV7B3C23RJEBNOENSCQ65VN7D4.jpg&h=1bf9d6c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我一定會守護這裏<br />\n<br />\n【讀者打氣】給黎智英的信繼續寄到本報，來信人為暫時無法張聲的「肥佬黎」申冤，也為香港一代傳媒大亨感到自豪。有女孩傳來親筆信，說一定要守護香港；有女士憑畫寄意，感謝他為這個家的付出。「感謝您一直以來為這個家的付出，為了香港的下一代，您選擇留下來承受這一切。」署名「香港讀者」的一位女子送上一幅由她繪畫的黎智英肖像，感謝他「在黑暗時刻仍堅持為香港燃點起這點光」。親筆信還有來自一位就讀小六的女學生，署名為「永遠愛香港的人，穿着黃衣的女孩」，信中畫了一名小女孩，她感謝黎智英盡心報道真相，她父母每天看新聞都非常生氣，「我不明白為甚麼政府對我們那麼壞，我們沒有做壞事吧！」儘管所有人都放棄香港，但她「一定會守護這裏的」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：陸委會轟除異己「港將走向煉獄」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港美麗因為有您<br />\n<br />\n黎生：<br />\n<br />\n感謝您一直以來為這個家的付出，<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：歐美聲援 彭斯促放政治犯： 控黎等於侮辱愛自由的人<br />\n<br />\n為了香港的下一代，您選擇留下來承受這一切。<br />\n<br />\n在黑暗時刻仍然堅持為香港燃點起這點光。<br />\n<br />\n香港之所以美麗，因為有您和一眾堅守家園的香港人。<br />\n<br />\n請保重。<br />\n<br />\n香港讀者上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ITUFTdKocemj6c6WxFfLfafseyo=/886x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MACANT66FRD5XEUEJ4VUQY2WTY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FITUFTdKocemj6c6WxFfLfafseyo%3D%2F886x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMACANT66FRD5XEUEJ4VUQY2WTY.jpg&h=4fec60f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/G270uZG09FXAidIfULCtvuhT0Ho=/1261x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MNIMR2UQSNCGJGZGYD4OQLU2GA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FG270uZG09FXAidIfULCtvuhT0Ho%3D%2F1261x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMNIMR2UQSNCGJGZGYD4OQLU2GA.jpg&h=ebf5b517&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n謝謝你的付出<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TwUt-VR9O2iIpdgtjPY7rGr7y3c=/1304x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TTIVEAAJGJAF3A2JNKQOY4OYM4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTwUt-VR9O2iIpdgtjPY7rGr7y3c%3D%2F1304x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTTIVEAAJGJAF3A2JNKQOY4OYM4.jpg&h=2d1ff627&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■5歲小朋友Erin親手繪製聖誕卡為黎智英打氣，祝福他身體健康，早日重獲自由。"},{"pid":"4c392563f42e8a7a5ed8fb460f145fcc68974122","tid":2311305,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T10:46:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVkwZqd5.jpg&amp;h=7ca7dfc2&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"11ad9ff49aac2765cf378e8a584cc38abaa100b2","tid":2311305,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T10:47:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2F057f373r%2Fimage.jpg&amp;h=c78f2cf9&amp;s=540\" />"}]}